2d:T617,AI call answering services in the UK range from £50 to £400 per month depending on features, call volume, and service level. Here is the complete breakdown of whoza.ai plans designed specifically for UK tradespeople:

<strong>Starter Plan: £59 per month</strong>
The Starter plan is designed for sole traders and small businesses with 1-2 employees. It includes unlimited call answering, 24/7 availability, WhatsApp delivery with Accept/Call Back/Decline buttons, and a custom greeting with your business name. This plan is ideal for plumbers, electricians, gas engineers, and locksmiths who receive 5 to 15 calls per day. There are no per-call charges. No hidden fees. Just £59 per month for unlimited coverage.

<strong>Growth Plan: £125 per month</strong>
The Growth plan adds team features and priority support. It includes everything in the Starter plan plus multiple team members, shared WhatsApp notifications, priority call handling, and advanced customisation options. This plan suits growing businesses with 2 to 5 employees who need to distribute leads among the team. It also includes priority customer support with faster response times.

<strong>Scale Plan: £399 per month</strong>
The Scale plan is designed for larger trade businesses with multiple vans, locations, or high call volumes. It includes all Growth features plus dedicated account management, custom conversation scripts, API access for CRM integration, and white-glove onboarding. This plan is for established businesses that need enterprise-level service and customisation.24:["$","section","section-0",{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-8","children":"AI Call Answering Plans and Pricing UK"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line mb-4","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2d"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr","row-0",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Starter Plan"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£59/month | Unlimited calls | WhatsApp delivery | 1 user | Ideal for solo traders"}]]}],["$","tr","row-1",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Growth Plan"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£125/month | Unlimited calls | Team notifications | Priority support | 2-5 users"}]]}],["$","tr","row-2",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Scale Plan"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£399/month | Unlimited calls | Custom scripts | API access | Dedicated manager"}]]}]]}]}]}],"$undefined",["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-emerald-500/10 border-l-4 border-emerald-500 rounded-r-xl p-6 my-6","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-emerald-200/90 font-medium leading-relaxed","children":"All plans include unlimited call answering, 24/7 availability, and WhatsApp delivery. No per-call charges. No hidden fees. No long-term contracts. Cancel anytime."}]}]]}]
2e:T4ef,The maths is simple. Let me show you exactly how the return on investment works for a typical UK tradesperson.

<strong>Conservative estimate:</strong>
- AI cost: £59 per month
- Average job value: £280
- Jobs needed to break even: 1 per month (0.2 per week)
- Realistic jobs captured: 3-5 per month
- Monthly revenue recovered: £840-£1,400
- Annual revenue recovered: £10,080-£16,800
- Net annual gain: £9,372-£16,092
- ROI: 1,321% to 2,274%

<strong>Realistic estimate (busy season):</strong>
- AI cost: £125 per month (Growth plan)
- Average job value: £350
- Jobs captured: 5-8 per month
- Monthly revenue recovered: £1,750-£2,800
- Annual revenue recovered: £21,000-£33,600
- Net annual gain: £19,500-£32,100
- ROI: 1,300% to 2,140%

These are not theoretical numbers. These are the actual results reported by whoza.ai users. Gary the plumber captured £6,800 in 4 weeks. Dave the sparky recovered £4,200 in 3 weeks. Mark the gas engineer recovered £6,650 in one month. Every single one of them broke even within the first week.

For a detailed breakdown of missed call costs, see our <a href="https://whoza.ai/blog/missed-call-recovery-trades-guide" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">Missed Call Recovery Guide</a>.25:["$","section","section-1",{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-8","children":"ROI Calculator: How Much Money Will You Make Back?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line mb-4","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2e"}}],"$undefined","$undefined","$undefined"]}]
2f:T6bc,Not all AI call answering services are transparent about pricing. Here are the hidden costs and red flags to watch for when evaluating providers:

<strong>Per-minute billing</strong>
Some services charge per minute of call time. This seems cheap at first — £0.10 per minute — but it adds up quickly. A 2-minute call is £0.20. Ten calls per day is £2. Twenty calls per day is £4. Over a month, that is £80-£120 in per-minute charges on top of the base fee. During busy periods or marketing campaigns, costs spike unpredictably. Fixed monthly pricing is always better for tradespeople.

<strong>Setup fees</strong>
Some providers charge £200-£500 for setup. This is unnecessary. whoza.ai has zero setup fees. You should not pay to connect your phone number and configure your greeting.

<strong>Overage charges</strong>
Some plans limit the number of calls or minutes per month. Exceed the limit and you pay overage fees. This is risky for tradespeople because call volumes fluctuate seasonally. A cold snap in January means boiler breakdowns spike. A summer heatwave means air conditioning enquiries flood in. You need unlimited calls to avoid nasty surprises.

<strong>Long-term contracts</strong>
Some providers lock you into 12-month contracts with cancellation fees. This is a red flag. You should be able to cancel anytime. whoza.ai offers monthly billing with no contracts. You can leave whenever you want — though most users never do because the ROI is too strong.

<strong>Email-only delivery</strong>
Some services deliver leads only by email. This is slow and inconvenient for tradespeople who are rarely at a desk. WhatsApp delivery is essential. If a service does not offer WhatsApp, look elsewhere.26:["$","section","section-2",{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-8","children":"Hidden Costs to Watch Out For"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line mb-4","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2f"}}],"$undefined",["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 mb-6","children":[["$","li","list-0",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":[["$","path","yps3ct",{"d":"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"}],["$","path","1pflzl",{"d":"m9 11 3 3L22 4"}],"$undefined"]}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/80","children":"Avoid per-minute billing — costs spike unpredictably during busy periods"}]]}],["$","li","list-1",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":[["$","path","yps3ct",{"d":"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"}],["$","path","1pflzl",{"d":"m9 11 3 3L22 4"}],"$undefined"]}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/80","children":"Avoid setup fees — configuration should be free"}]]}],["$","li","list-2",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":["$L30","$L31","$undefined"]}],"$L32"]}],"$L33","$L34"]}],"$undefined"]}]
35:T652,To understand the true value of AI call answering, you need to compare it to the alternatives. Here is how the costs stack up:

<strong>Do nothing (voicemail only)</strong>
Cost: £0 per month. Revenue loss: £50,000-£70,000 per year. This is the most expensive option because the cost of missed calls far exceeds any subscription fee. You are essentially paying £50,000 per year in lost revenue to save £59 per month.

<strong>Virtual receptionist service</strong>
Cost: £400-£600 per month. These services use human operators in call centres to answer your phone. They work 9-5, go home in the evening, and charge extra for weekend coverage. The quality is variable — different operators answer each call, and they may not understand trade terminology. Over a year, this costs £4,800-£7,200.

<strong>Hire a part-time receptionist</strong>
Cost: £800-£1,200 per month. A part-time receptionist works 2-3 days per week. They cover some calls but miss evenings, weekends, and the days they are not working. They also require desk space, a phone, a computer, and training. Over a year, this costs £9,600-£14,400 plus overheads.

<strong>Hire a full-time receptionist</strong>
Cost: £1,667-£2,500 per month. As discussed earlier, the total first-year cost is £26,000-£35,000. This is simply unaffordable for most small trade businesses.

<strong>AI call answering</strong>
Cost: £59-£399 per month. Unlimited calls. 24/7 coverage. WhatsApp delivery. No overheads. No contracts. One recovered job per month pays for the service. This is the only option that makes financial sense for most tradespeople.27:["$","section","section-3",{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-8","children":"How Does AI Cost Compare to Alternatives?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-white/80 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line mb-4","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$35"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr","row-0",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Voicemail only"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£0/month | £50,000-£70,000/year lost revenue"}]]}],["$","tr","row-1",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Virtual receptionist"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£400-£600/month | £4,800-£7,200/year | 9-5 only"}]]}],["$","tr","row-2",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Part-time human"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£800-£1,200/month | £9,600-£14,400/year | Partial coverage"}]]}],["$","tr","row-3",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"Full-time human"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£1,667-£2,500/month | £26,000-£35,000/year | 9-5 only"}]]}],["$","tr","row-4",{"className":"border-b border-white/10 last:border-0","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-white/70 w-1/3","children":"AI call answering"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-white/90","children":"£59-£399/month | £708-£4,788/year | 24/7 unlimited"}]]}]]}]}]}],"$undefined","$L36"]}]
